1. Create src/cli.ts that reads JSON from stdin, parses it, runs processScenario, writes JSON to stdout. On unknown item type, write an error message to stderr and exit 1.
2. Add unknown-type detection. Simplest approach: validate input scenario before calling processScenario. For each quote step, check every item.type is in a known-types set (or BASE_PREMIUM keys). If unknown, throw new Error(`unknown item type: ${type}`). In cli.ts, wrap in try/catch and exit 1 with stderr write on error.

